		<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-autospace: none">
		<font face="Arial" color="#008000">Looking for graduate students/RAs to 
		participate the following projects: (i). IoT security; (ii). Approximate 
		computing for error-resilient applications (e.g., pattern recognition, 
		data mining and synthesis); (iii) Smart hardware design.</font></p>
		<p class="style2" style="text-autospace: none">
		&nbsp;</p>
		<p class="style2" style="text-autospace: none">
		CUHK CS&amp;E students supervised by Prof. Xu won Championship in
		<a href="http://www.aidc.org.cn/reigning.jsp">Huawei Cup</a> and it 
		comes with the grand prize of 15,000 RMB, at the annual smart design 
		collegiate competition in the Great China area, 2015. [<a href="http://www.aidc.org.cn/downloads/2015&#21326;&#20026;&#26479;&#20915;&#36187;&#33719;&#22870;&#21517;&#21333;&#20844;&#31034;.pdf">link</a>]</p>
		<p class="style2" style="text-autospace: none">
		CUHK CS&amp;E students supervised by Prof. Xu won the first prize at
		<a href="http://www.hkchallengecup.com">Hong Kong Challenge Cup</a> and 
		rank #1 in the IT category, 2015. [<a href="http://www.hkchallengecup.com/#!about1/cnup">link</a>]</p>
		<p class="style2" style="text-autospace: none">
		Yannan's paper was nominated for Best Paper Award at
		<a href="http://www.dac.com">ACM/IEEE Design Automation Conference</a> 
		(DAC), 2015. There are only 5 out of 789 submissions nominated! [<a href="http://www2.dac.com/events/eventdetails.aspx?id=182-26">link</a>]</p>
		<p class="style2" style="text-autospace: none">
		Call for papers in
		<a href="http://ieee-ceda.org/images/design-test/CFP-Approximate.pdf">
		IEEE Design &amp; Test Special Issue on Approximate Computing</a>.</p>
		<p class="style2" style="text-autospace: none">
